title: Launch Roundup: SpaceX to launch two Starlink missions; China to launch Chang Zheng 5
summary: A brand new week of spaceflight is approaching with SpaceX preparing to launch two Starlink missions, China getting ready to send two payloads to orbit, including one on the powerful Chang Zheng 5 (CZ-5) rocket, and Roscosmos preparing to launch Russian-built satellites to orbit atop Soyuz.
